# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rust (fulgur-native/)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Build artifacts of the FFI shim. rust's default output dir.
fulgur-native/target/

# We DO commit Cargo.lock — the .dll/.so/.dylib that ends up in the NuGet
# package must reproduce bit-for-bit across machines, so we want every
# consumer to resolve the same dependency graph.
!fulgur-native/Cargo.lock

# rust-analyzer / IDE caches
.idea/
*.rs.bk
**/*.rs.bk

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .NET / dotnet CLI
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Standard SDK output dirs (covers every project, including examples/).
**/bin/
**/obj/

# NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

# Test runners
TestResults/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
*.trx
*.testlog
.coverage
CoverletOutput*/

# Roslyn / .NET SDK generated
*.assets.json
*.nuget.dgspec.json
*.nuget.g.props
*.nuget.g.targets
*.nuget.cache
project.assets.json
project.nuget.cache

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BenchmarkDotNet artifacts (rebuilt on every `dotnet run -- --full`)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/
*.BDN.*.log
FulgurNET.Benchmarks*/bin/

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local dev logs and scratch
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (keep bench-results.md — that's the published headline numbers)
bench-*.log
build-*.log
*.dmp
*.pdb.bak
scratch/
playground/
*.pdf.bak

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IDEs and editors
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
*.userprefs
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Rider
.idea/
*.sln.iml

# VS Code
.vscode/

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS junk
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_view.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# macOS / Linux
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Misc build / format artifacts
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exp
*.ilk
*.tmp
*.dll.config
publish/
